title: Amen glory to #God I claim it, and I receive it in the Mighty name of #Jesus! We all need to start speaking...

attachments.displayName: Amen glory to #God I claim it, and I receive it in the Mighty name of #Jesus! We all need to start speaking off the negative, and start speaking positive, we need to speak of poverty and start to speak that we are rich not just rich in money but rich in the word, we need to get out of the darkness, for we are children of #God and start walking in the light. We need to walk by faith and not by sight; for those that are still fighting to keep one door open, #STOP and let #God shut that door so He can open another, trust Him He knows what's better for his children. Stop being afraid, #God didn't give us fear, start standing up, stop with the doubt why are you doubting if you know that God is real, if you know #God never left us and he got us through all of our trails start believing and start trusting! Amen! ❤
